column1: CS4222 DEMO for collecting accelerometer data (version 3.0.0)
Long press the left pin to start the collection process (green led goes ON)
Long press the right pin to stop the collection process (green led goes OFF)
All accelerometer data are saved in the external flash

column2: the accelerometer data is displayed. Two lines are associated with each sample:

column1: Line one shows the raw values of the collected data
Line two shows the respective values as written to the flash
Note that the first value is the timeLeft: Pin 0
